map_npcs.name: Head Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Have you spoken with Carl yet?
He should be near the tents just to the South.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, hello there! You must be {player}. 
Please do take a look around our humble Hub.
Oh, and you'll want to speak with Carl.
He'll have your ID. {objective:Speak with Carl}
And before you go, take these!

map_npcs.name: Researcher Carl
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Gah, I'm busy, could you come back later?
...
Oh.
Wait are you that new employee?
One sec, here's your ID. {objective:Return to the Head Researcher}

map_npcs.name: Head Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Have you had any luck investigating that sound?
Please let me know once you've investigated thoroughly!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Ah, now that you've got your ID, you should be all sorted.
Get out there and explore!
**BOOM**
Oh my! What was that?
Please go investigate that noise.{objective:Investigate the Crater}
It sounds like it came from the West...

map_npcs.name: Guard George
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Nuh, uh, I need to see some ID buddy.

map_npcs.name: Guard Bob
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Sorry, still can't let you through!
Maybe try talking to the Head Researcher or Carl about your ID?
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Sorry, we can't let you pass without ID!

map_npcs.name: Guard Bob
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, you got your ID? That's great!
Sorry for needing to keep you locked up in here.

map_npcs.name: Guard George
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Ugh, Bob better not be slacking off again...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Hey! How did you get out here?
I'm taking you right back to the hub!

map_npcs.name: Researcher Gavin
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Welp, back to staring at this wall again.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: I've got some free time, let's battle!

map_npcs.name: Raider Sasha
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: I guess you were pretty tough after all...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Oh, I bet you're *sooooo* tough. Let's see you prove it.

map_npcs.name: Raider Nina
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: I'm no one suspicious, I swear!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Hmmm, I bet if I stacked some barrels high enough...
Huh? Who goes there!?

map_npcs.name: Head Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Feel free to come back here and rest any time.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Do stay safe out there, I appreciate all you're doing for us!

map_npcs.name: Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Probably best that you don't go in there for now...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Hmmm, we're getting some strange readings from within this cave.

map_npcs.name: Impatient Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Hey, wait your turn, I was here first!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Gah, I wish the construction team would let me know what's going on in there...

map_shops.greeting_dialogue: Welcome to my store. Buy whatever you need below!
